<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

  <head>
    <!--Meta Data-->
    <%- include('partial/title.ejs'); %> 

    <% if (data.NODE_ENV == 'production') { %>
      <!-- Production Stylesheets -->
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/production/css/about.min.css">

    <% }else { %>
      <!-- Development Stylesheets -->
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/bootstrap.min.css">
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/fontawesome.min.css">
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/responsive.css">
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/select2.min.css">
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/spacing.css">
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/style.css">
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/owl.carousel.min.css">
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/bootstrap-datepicker.min.css">
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/magnific-popup.css">
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/header.css">
      
    <% } %>
  </head>

  <body onLoad="typeWriter()">
    <!--Header-->
    <%- include('partial/header.ejs', {data: data }); %>
    

    <!--About Start-->
    <div class="about-page pt_60 pb_30">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <h3>Our Mission</h3>
            <p>At DocConnect, our mission is to revolutionize the healthcare industry by providing an innovative and user-friendly appointment system that enhances accessibility and efficiency for both patients and healthcare providers. <br></p>

            <p>We are committed to leveraging cutting-edge technology to streamline the appointment process and ensure seamless communication between patients and medical professionals.<br></p>
            <p>Our goal is to empower individuals to take control of their health by making appointment scheduling easier, faster, and more convenient than ever before.</p>
            <br>

            <h3>Our Vision</h3>
            <p>Our goal is to create a comprehensive platform that not only facilitates appointment booking but also offers advanced features such as ambulance booking with tracing and real-time updates. Our platform provides a seamless appointment booking experience for patients, allowing them to easily schedule appointments with their preferred healthcare providers. Whether it's for a routine check-up or a specialist consultation, patients can book appointments at their convenience.</p>

            <p>Our platform is designed with a focus on efficiency and safety. By streamlining the appointment and ambulance booking process, we aim to reduce wait times and minimize delays in medical care.<br></p>
            <p>With these features and our commitment to innovation, DocConnect is poised to transform the healthcare industry. Together, we can build a future where healthcare is accessible to all and emergencies are handled with speed and efficiency."<br></p>
            <br>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!--About End-->

    <!--Footer-->
    <%- include('partial/footer.ejs'); %>

    <script>
      var i = 0;
      var txt = 'WELCOME TO DocConnect';
      var speed = 60;
      function typeWriter() {
        if (i < txt.length) {
          document.getElementById("typeit").innerHTML += txt.charAt(i);
          i++;
          setTimeout(typeWriter, speed);
        }
      }
    </script>

    <!-- JavaScript -->
    <script defer src="assets/lib/js/jquery-3.4.1.min.js"></script>
    <script defer src="/assets/lib/js/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script defer src="assets/lib/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script defer src="assets/lib/js/all.min.js"></script>
    <script defer src="assets/lib/js/select2.full.min.js"></script>
    <script defer src="assets/js/about.js"></script>

  </body>
</html>